  "detailed_description": "<strong>■Middle school student, Girl! is!</strong><br>The girl, who was frustrated by her uncle's overprotection, wakes up in a strange forest. All she got is only a machete. <br>\"Where am I? but... first of all, hungry!\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/c2d6642c36e748e2d7442b13b2a02197.poster.avif?t=1729847869\" width=500 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/c2d6642c36e748e2d7442b13b2a02197.webm?t=1729847869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/c2d6642c36e748e2d7442b13b2a02197.mp4?t=1729847869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>■Enjoy a simple and short story that saves the world!</strong><br>The girl has no experience of reincarnation, no special ability. Just a little survival knowledge and a healthy body.<br>But coincidence, necessity, and small warm hearts come together, and the girl...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/d412e96b90fe8c7294803dab4ef94bd1.poster.avif?t=1729847869\" width=500 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/d412e96b90fe8c7294803dab4ef94bd1.webm?t=1729847869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/d412e96b90fe8c7294803dab4ef94bd1.mp4?t=1729847869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>■Easy and simple battle</strong><br>Avoid enemies when they come, and if you see a gap, join forces in machete and hit them!<br>Often, using other tool than machete makes it easier to fight battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/41c7ab3913cf479d078650bc65f2f031.avif?t=1729847869\" width=400 height=200 /></span><br><br><strong>■Try out various production recipes.</strong><br>You can make many things with materials from monsters or your surroundings.<br>Make, test, and challenge the next boss!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/f870b5b8528d4789422713942c82b130.poster.avif?t=1729847869\" width=500 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/f870b5b8528d4789422713942c82b130.webm?t=1729847869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/f870b5b8528d4789422713942c82b130.mp4?t=1729847869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>■Eat a balanced diet.</strong><br>Understand the role of the four major nutrients, and maintain a healthy body with a balanced diet.<br>Picky food is really, really bad!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>■Middle school student, Girl! is!</strong><br>The girl, who was frustrated by her uncle's overprotection, wakes up in a strange forest. All she got is only a machete. <br>\"Where am I? but... first of all, hungry!\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/c2d6642c36e748e2d7442b13b2a02197.poster.avif?t=1729847869\" width=500 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/c2d6642c36e748e2d7442b13b2a02197.webm?t=1729847869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/c2d6642c36e748e2d7442b13b2a02197.mp4?t=1729847869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>■Enjoy a simple and short story that saves the world!</strong><br>The girl has no experience of reincarnation, no special ability. Just a little survival knowledge and a healthy body.<br>But coincidence, necessity, and small warm hearts come together, and the girl...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/d412e96b90fe8c7294803dab4ef94bd1.poster.avif?t=1729847869\" width=500 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/d412e96b90fe8c7294803dab4ef94bd1.webm?t=1729847869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2512910/extras/d412e96b90fe8c7294803dab4ef94bd1.mp4?t=1729847869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>■Easy and simple battle</strong><br>Avoid enemies when they come, and if you see a gap, join forces in machete and hit them!<br>Often, using other tool than machete makes it easier to fight battles.<